Back to Board of Directors




Theodore M. Solso
Independent Lead Director, General Motors Company and  Retired Chairman & CEO Cummins, Inc.Director Since: 2012






Mr. Solso has served as the Independent Lead Director of the GM Board of Directors since January 2016.  He had been the Non-Executive Chairman of the GM Board of Directors since January 2014.  Mr. Solso served as Chairman and Chief Executive Officer of Cummins, Inc. (“Cummins”) from 2000 until his retirement in 2011. Prior to becoming Chairman and CEO, Mr. Solso held various other senior management roles at Cummins, including President and Chief Operating Officer from 1995 through 2000.
Mr. Solso is also Lead Director at Ball Corporation.

























































































